text: Aamer Jamal (born 5 July 1996) is a Pakistani cricketer. He made his first- class debut for Pakistan Television in the 2018–19 Quaid-e-Azam Trophy on 1 September 2018. He made his List A debut for Pakistan Television in the 2018–19 Quaid-e-Azam One Day Cup on 22 September 2018. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Pakistani cricketers Category:Pakistan Television cricketers Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
